EU Says It Trusts Italy Will Take Needed Measures

-- B y   J o n e s   H a y d e n
-- 
2011-10-07T10:26:29Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-07/eu-says-it-trusts-italy-will-take-needed-measures.html
The European Union said it trusts
that Italy will taken needed budget measures as soon as
possible.  “We trust the Italian authorities to take the necessary
measures as soon as possible,” and EU spokesman told reporters
in Brussels today. Taking the measures would help “bring back
trust,” he said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jones Hayden at 
 jhayden1@bloomberg.net  